191
0:08:38.06,000 --> 0:08:39,000
J'ai cofondé un programme

192
0:08:39.82,000 --> 0:08:43,000
appelé Finances Émotions Émancipation Liberté,

193
0:08:44.42,000 --> 0:08:45,000
